Crystal brick, known for its crystal-clear appearance and unique optical effects, is a high-quality building material. Made of high-quality raw glass, it is processed uniquely to form a complex, transparent brick body. Crystal brick usually has a clear and transparent appearance, but it can also be colored in various colors by adding pigments. Regarding surface patterns, decorations such as textures, designs, or three-dimensional patterns can increase the artistic sense of crystal tiles.

Crystal brick has excellent light permeability, filling the room with bright natural light. At the same time, it is also waterproof, easy to clean, and wear-resistant, making it an ideal choice for decorating walls and floors. Crystal brick is solid and stable, suitable for interior decoration, such as living room, dining room, bathroom, etc. Its unique light refraction effect can add a sense of luxury and modernity to the space.
